Australian CGT Calculator


CGT Calculation Formula


Capital Gain = Net Sale Proceeds − Cost Base Net Sale Proceeds = Sale Price − Sale Costs Cost Base = Purchase Price + Purchase Costs + Capital Improvements Discounted Gain = Capital Gain × 50% (if held for more than 12 months) CGT Payable = Discounted Gain × Marginal Tax Rate (%)




&lt;div class="col-md-4"&gt;
  &lt;div class="card"&gt;
    &lt;div class="card-header"&gt;
      &lt;h5&gt;Input Parameters&lt;/h5&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="card-body"&gt;
      &lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
        &lt;label for="purchase_price" class="form-label"&gt;Purchase Price (AUD):&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input type="number" class="form-control" id="purchase_price" value="0" step="0.01"&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
        &lt;label for="sale_price" class="form-label"&gt;Sale Price (AUD):&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input type="number" class="form-control" id="sale_price" value="0" step="0.01"&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
        &lt;label for="purchase_costs" class="form-label"&gt;Purchase Costs:&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input type="number" class="form-control" id="purchase_costs" value="0" step="0.01"&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
        &lt;label for="sale_costs" class="form-label"&gt;Sale Costs:&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input type="number" class="form-control" id="sale_costs" value="0" step="0.01"&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
        &lt;label for="capital_improvements" class="form-label"&gt;Capital Improvements:&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input type="number" class="form-control" id="capital_improvements" value="0" step="0.01"&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
        &lt;label for="purchase_date" class="form-label"&gt;Purchase Date:&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input type="date" class="form-control" id="purchase_date"&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
        &lt;label for="sale_date" class="form-label"&gt;Sale Date:&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input type="date" class="form-control" id="sale_date"&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="mb-3 form-check"&gt;
        &lt;input type="checkbox" class="form-check-input" id="discount_eligible" checked&gt;
        &lt;label class="form-check-label" for="discount_eligible"&gt;
          Held more than 12 months (50% CGT discount applies)
        &lt;/label&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div class="mb-3"&gt;
        &lt;label for="marginal_tax_rate" class="form-label"&gt;Your Marginal Tax Rate (%):&lt;/label&gt;
        &lt;input type="number" class="form-control" id="marginal_tax_rate" value="37" step="0.1" min="0" max="100"&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="calculateCGT()"&gt;Calculate CGT&lt;/button&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;!-- RESULT CARD --&gt;
&lt;div class="col-md-8"&gt;
  &lt;div class="card"&gt;
    &lt;div class="card-header"&gt;
      &lt;h5&gt;CGT Summary&lt;/h5&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="card-body"&gt;
      &lt;div id="result" class="alert alert-info"&gt;
        Enter your values and click "Calculate CGT" to see the results.
      &lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;div id="detailed_results" style="display: none;"&gt;
